title: Out Of Bounds-80`s Anthony Michael Hall
description:
Movie Description
An Iowa farmboy accidentally stumbles into a terrifying world of murder and drug dealing when he mistakenly picks up the wrong bag at the airport and finds himself holding a million dollars worth of heroin. Police think him a dealer and the actual dealers want him dead in this thrilling 1986 actioner that gave comedic actor Anthony Michael Hall to spread his wings.

Credits 
Cast: Anthony Michael Hall 
Director: Richard Tuggle 

Synopsis
A bored midwestern farmboy flies to Los Angeles to visit his beloved brother and take a wide-eyed look at big city life. Unfortunately, he grabs the wrong bag at the airport and ends up with a sizeable cachet of smuggled heroin. The police now think he&#039;s a drug courier, and the dealers want him dead for stealing what&#039;s rightfully theirs. With nowhere to run, this country boy better learn city ways fast.
